and we moved a lot.

131
00:24:52,928 --> 00:24:57,476
So, I guess you can say
I don't really have home town.

132
00:24:57,672 --> 00:24:58,892
That's kind of funny actually.

133
00:25:00,450 --> 00:25:01,550
How so?

134
