141
00:25:38,610 --> 00:25:40,622
So, you left it up to chance, hey?

142
00:25:41,363 --> 00:25:42,428
Yeah.

143
00:25:43,256 --> 00:25:44,463
No.

144
00:25:45,278 --> 00:25:46,905
I actually had the time on my own.

145
00:25:47,694 --> 00:25:52,098
Couldn't afford a bus ticket to
Los Angeles, so ended up here.

146
00:25:54,473 --> 00:25:58,294
