opened up, Horseshoe lounge.

148
00:26:06,085 --> 00:26:07,387
Horseshoe, eh?

149
00:26:09,186 --> 00:26:11,647
Yeah, I work the bar.

150
00:26:12,237 --> 00:26:13,620
Do some security work.

151
00:26:14,225 --> 00:26:16,686
- So, you work late nights?
- Yeah.

152
00:26:21,328 --> 00:26:25,420
