168
00:30:18,095 --> 00:30:21,223
Nothing really, just always
wanted to see the Ocean.

169
00:30:21,710 --> 00:30:23,866
That makes the two of us actually.

170
00:30:24,234 --> 00:30:26,004
Never been?
Never.

171
00:30:26,504 --> 00:30:31,378
