175
00:30:48,861 --> 00:30:53,199
She had a nervous breakdown
when my dad passed away and...

176
00:30:54,245 --> 00:30:57,020
...she's under a lot of medication.

177
00:30:57,196 --> 00:31:01,782
Well, it's a long sad story.

178
00:31:04,546 --> 00:31:08,110
Hey, you'll be all right.

179
00:31:10,897 --> 00:31:15,713
Well, yeah, I just prefer not to talk
about it, you know.

180
00:31:15,955 --> 00:31:18,965
Yeah, I hear ya...

181
00:32:17,885 --> 00:32:19,564
Hi Alex... how are things here?

182
00:32:19,589 --> 00:32:20,641
