00:32:31,727 --> 00:32:32,728
How ya doing?

190
00:32:34,220 --> 00:32:36,556
Pretty good?
Just waiting to get paid.

191
00:32:36,581 --> 00:32:38,708
What did you do? Hit a jackpot?

192
00:32:38,733 --> 00:32:40,242
