198
00:32:55,966 --> 00:32:57,710
Great, thank you.

199
00:32:57,735 --> 00:32:59,411
Let me know if you need anything.

200
00:32:59,436 --> 00:33:01,543
I sure will, darling,
you have a good evening.

201
00:33:57,910 --> 00:34:01,206
So, got a plan for you, Chloe.

202
00:34:01,828 --> 00:34:03,587
Oh yeah? And what's that?

203
00:34:04,477 --> 00:34:09,873
Well, you got a job offer
if you are interested.

204
00:34:11,162 --> 00:34:13,124
I'm interested.

205
