234
00:36:12,962 --> 00:36:15,083
I'd keep an eye on him and his girlfriend.

235
00:36:15,108 --> 00:36:18,641
Oh, come on Bruno, he's a good kid,
he reminds me of my son.

236
00:36:18,666 --> 00:36:21,937
Yeah, but there is something else going
on with him, I don't know what it is yet.

237
00:36:21,962 --> 00:36:24,042
But my gut tells me he's hiding something.

238
00:36:24,107 --> 00:36:26,140
I can see it in his eyes.

239
00:36:26,180 --> 00:36:28,140
Well then, you see something I don't.

240
00:36:29,892 --> 00:36:33,103
Don't worry about it.
I got your back on this, boss.

241
00:36:33,128 --> 00:36:36,162
All right, well, let's go over here
to Salles and grab a bite.

242
00:36:37,057 --> 00:36:37,975
Sounds good to me.

243
00:36:40,034 --> 00:36:41,922
So how much money did you win?

244
00:36:43,559 --> 00:36:45,321
