20.

248
00:36:53,376 --> 00:36:55,246
Shit, take it to the bank.

249
00:36:56,448 --> 00:36:57,866
I will.

250
00:36:58,127 --> 00:37:00,812
So, did you take care
of those girls for me?

251
00:37:01,140 --> 00:37:02,489
I did, I did.

252
00:37:03,398 --> 00:37:05,978
You did?
Yes, no more problem with that.

253
00:37:06,158 --> 00:37:08,987
I had a little problem
at the bar tonight.

254
00:37:09,189 --> 00:37:10,209
What?

255
00:37:11,852 --> 00:37:13,298
